out of the airport to make way for new hangars like those at left. HARRY CHASE 
/ Los Angeles Times; Map, Map shows current and proposed uses under Torrance's 
airport redevelopment project., GEORGE CAREY / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
