</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
61 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSWIRE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Yugoslav basketball star Drazen Petrovic and the Portland Trail Blazers have 
reached a contract agreement. 
</P>
<P>
The guard flew to Portland from Spain, where he was playing for Club Real 
Madrid. 
</P>
<P>
Warren Legarie, Petrovic's agent, said the contract could make Petrovic the 
highest-paid of the European players who will join the National Basketball 
Assn. this season. 
</P>
</TEXT>
