<HEADLINE>
<P>
SPOTLIGHT / COMMERCIAL REAL ESTATE: FOCUS: 1 CITY BLVD. WEST BUILDING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Formerly the Bank of America Tower, this 18-story building was completed nearly 
20 years ago. The lobby was renovated in 1987 and enlarged. The building is 
located within The City in Orange, a development which also includes a regional 
mall, 15 restaurants, 10 movie theaters, a health spa and the Doubletree Hotel. 
The tower is 78% leased. 
</P>
<P>
FACTS AND FIGURES 
</P>
