</P>
<P>
Developer: City Management Corp. (Agent for Metropolitan Life Insurance Co.) 
</P>
<P>
Architect: Naramore, Bain, Brady &amp; Johanson 
</P>
<P>
Primary Contractor: Turner Construction Co. 
</P>
<P>
Broker: Tishman West Cos. 
</P>
<P>
Financing: Metropolitan Life 
</P>
<P>
